Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10}來 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10}長久以來真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10}小爽是找稀有CD的天才呢
